- Video data is given in table
- Compare the tags of review with the video tags
- Recommend videos on the basis of those tags
- If not found, then omit the last tag and research video, then recommend, if still not found, leave the K:V
- Each video will be having 4 tags-> department, domain, attribute, subject and so will the review.
- Video details will contain -> name, thumbnail_url, video_url, quiz, tag
- watchlist will contain -> video_details_id, hotel_id, is_watched, show_on

5 - department
15 - domain
21 - attribute
